==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hands
<hw>hands</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a person's power or
discretionary action; <as>as, my fate is in your
<ex>hands</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> custody.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The force of workers available; <as>as, all
<ex>hands</ex> on deck</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> work force, manpower, men.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><q>A dictionary containing a natural history requires too many
<qex>hands</qex>, as well as too much time, ever to be hoped for.</q>
<rj><qau>Locke.</qau></rj></p>

<p><ent>Handsaw</ent>⟦br⟧
